<div class="container">

    <p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

    <h1>Posts</h1>
    <div class="mb-4">
        <%= render 'form', post: @post %>
    </div>
    <ul class="posts list-unstyled p-0 ">
        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
            <li class="post d-flex p-3  py-4">
                <%= image_tag 'https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/HASH', size: "48x48", alt: "Profile picture", :class => "me-3" %>
                <div ><%= post.content %></div>
            </li>
        <% end %>
        <li class="post d-flex p-3  ">
            <%= image_tag 'https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/HASH', size: "48x48", alt: "Profile picture", :class => "me-3" %>
            <div>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. <i>Quamquam te quidem video minime esse deterritum.</i> Virtutis, magnitudinis animi, patientiae, fortitudinis fomentis dolor mitigari solet. Illum mallem levares, quo optimum atque humanissimum virum, Cn.  </p>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>

</div>

